gh Custer State Park, a popular and scenic hiking, biking, and fishing destination in southwest South Dakota", "type": ["still image"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021757382/"}], "resource": {"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/idhi/batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01/data/sn88056158/00415666342/1910082301/0682.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:idhi:batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01:data:sn88056158:00415666342:1910082301:0677/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/idhi/batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01/data/sn88056158/00415666342/1910082301/0682.pdf", "segment_count": 8, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88056158/1910-08-23/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}, "resources": [{"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/idhi/batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01/data/sn88056158/00415666342/1910082301/0682.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:idhi:batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01:data:sn88056158:00415666342:1910082301:0677/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/idhi/batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01/data/sn88056158/00415666342/1910082301/0682.pdf", "segment_count": 8, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88056158/1910-08-23/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/idhi/batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01/data/sn88056158/00415666342/1910082301/0682.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88056158/1910-08-23/ed-1/?sp=6"], "batch": ["idhi_kellerman_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "composite_location": ["0/united states/", "1/united states/idaho/", "2/united states/idaho/custer/", "3/united states/idaho/custer/challis/"], "contributor": ["idaho state historical society"], "date": "1910-08-23", "dates": ["1910-08-23"], "description": ["THE RELATION OF RAILROAD RATES TO GENERAL BUSINESS ed the ton An or the wage Increases except a small amount were not in force during this period and from now on these will to To the Business Man ter how objectionable an advance In freight rates may be to us personally we must recognize that an improve ment In general business is dependent on a betterment of operating and financial conditions of the railroads That the operating results are most unsatisfactory Is readily seen by the latest INTERSTATE COMMERCE COMMISSION reports which show that for the nine months ended April 1st 1910 eleven railroad systems all West and North of a line drawn from Chicago to St Louis compared with the same roads for the same period in the previous year had their gross earnings increased about 5000000000 while their net earnings Bhowed a de crease of 350000000 and for the month of March on the same compari son they show an increase of 7000 00000 In gross and a decrease of 96500000 In net earnings Attention is cnlled to the fact that No mat Creally increase the operating These same railroads had their taxes Increased over the previous year"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-07-06T12:37:24.651Z", "group": ["ndnp/idhi", "idaho-state-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88056158/1910-08-23/ed-1/?sp=6", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:idhi:batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01:data:sn88056158:00415666342:1910082301:0682/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=412&w=281", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:idhi:batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01:data:sn88056158:00415666342:1910082301:0682/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=825&w=562", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/idhi/batch_idhi_kellerman_ver01/data/sn88056158/00415666